Salgado Tells Russia’s Siluanov Spanish Banking Industry Stable

-- B y   P a u l   A b e l s k y
-- 
2011-10-10T11:59:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/salgado-tells-russia-s-siluanov-spanish-banking-industry-stable.html
Spain ’s banking industry has a
“sufficient safety margin and is ready to operate under current
conditions,” Finance Minister  Elena Salgado  told her Russian
counterpart Anton Siluanov, according to a statement published
on the Russian Finance Ministry’s website after their meeting in
Moscow today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
